data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath 3 car garage in the well desired Hualapai Foothill Estates Subdivision.  Home features a split floor plan. Large kitchen with lots of counter space, pantry and refrigerator. Casual dining with seating at the counter as well. Laundry room with washer, dryer and sink. Backyard is set for entertaining with large covered patio, a large wood pergola, pizza oven and so much more.  Fully fenced with block wall for privacy, RV parking and shed.
